item.title: Contact
item.description: Getting in touch Below you can find some pointers for contacting us, as well as getting in touch with the community. Issues and Bug Reports For any bug reports, please first consult the main Github repositories : https://github.com/fullstackhero/. Chances are that a similar issue may have already been posted by other users in the past. Github has an excellent search function, which may help find existing answers to your questions.
